  .card
    .card-body
      h3 Overview
      p Due to the widespread use of <code>&lt;table&gt;</code>. elements across third-party widgets like calendars and date pickers, Bootstrap's tables are <strong>opt-in</strong>. Add the base class <code>.table</code> to any <code>&lt;table&gt;</code>, then extend with our optional modifier classes or custom styles. All table styles are not inherited in Bootstrap, meaning any nested tables can be styled independent from the parent.
      p Using the most basic table markup, here's how <code>.table</code>-based tables look in Bootstrap.

      .bd-example
        table.table
          thead
            tr
              th(scope='col') #
              th(scope='col') First
              th(scope='col') Last
              th(scope='col') Handle
          tbody
            tr
              th(scope='row') 1
              td Mark
              td Otto
              td @mdo
            tr
              th(scope='row') 2
              td Jacob
              td Thornton
              td @fat
            tr
              th(scope='row') 3
              td(colspan='2') Larry the Bird
              td @twitter

      pre
        code.language-html
          | &lt;table class="table"&gt;
          |   &lt;thead&gt;
          |     &lt;tr&gt;
          |       &lt;th scope="col"&gt;#&lt;/th&gt;
          |       &lt;th scope="col"&gt;First&lt;/th&gt;
          |       &lt;th scope="col"&gt;Last&lt;/th&gt;
          |       &lt;th scope="col"&gt;Handle&lt;/th&gt;
          |     &lt;/tr&gt;
          |   &lt;/thead&gt;
